142
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:41,900
 On ništa ne oduzima od nas, sve nam daje.

143
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:45,300
 On postaje dio nas.

144
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:48,900
 A mi postajemo dio njega.

145
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:54,300
 Nekad ljeti dođem u Hrvatsku.

146
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:57,700
 Bio sam u Dubrovniku.

147
00:12:57,700 --> 00:13:01,100
 Kad sunce sija,

148
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:03,900
