149
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:07,500
 glava mi je pocrveni.

150
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:12,100
 Zato što sunčeva svijetla spada na mene.

151
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:16,500
 I ja ne potamnim vrlo brzo.

152
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:22,500
 Crvena, tamno-crvena, onda tek smeđa.

153
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:28,500
 Na isti način kako ne možemo primiti sunce

154
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:33,500
